# ============================================================
#  Crypto Intelligence Terminal - frontend env (optional)
# ============================================================
#
#  ZERO CONFIG ON VERCEL
#  ---------------------
#  Deploy as-is. Snapshots are served by the in-app Next.js
#  route /api/snapshot which talks to Binance directly. No
#  backend service is required.
#
#  OPTIONAL: configure symbols
SYMBOLS=BTCUSDT,ETHUSDT,SOLUSDT
#
#  OPTIONAL: point at the FastAPI backend instead
#  -----------------------------------------------
#  Use these only if you self-host the persistent FastAPI
#  service (which adds rolling-window normalization and a
#  WebSocket stream). Leave them blank on Vercel.
#NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE=https://your-api.example.com
#NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=wss://your-api.example.com/api/ws
